Troubleshooting
Issue: ModuleNotFoundError for yaml or colorama

Solution: Run pip3 install pyyaml colorama --user
Issue: No patterns detected in logs

Solution: Check that keywords in patterns.yaml match log content (case-insensitive)
Issue: Permission denied when running scripts

Solution: Ensure scripts are executable: chmod +x *.py
Issue: Colors not displaying correctly

Solution: Colorama should handle this, but try: export TERM=xterm-256color
